**1. HTML Modification:**

Add a button element following the “Early Iterations” section (ideally right before the main body of the page):

```html
<button id="revealIterationsButton">Show Iterative Process</button>
```

**2. Initial State - Disable Automatic Animation**

We’ll start by disabling the automatic triggering entirely until the button interacts. Modify JS:

```javascript
document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', ()=> { //Ensure everything loads first
  const revealBtn = document.getElementById('revealIterationsButton');
  revealBtn.disabled = true; //Disable auto trigger
})
